data.title: "Hollywood Couples" Jack Lemon & Felicia Far (TV Episode 2001)
data.meta_description: Jack Lemon & Felicia Far: With Jack Lemmon. Dive into the details of Jack Lemmon's film career and his pursuit of Felicia Farr. From meeting on the set of 3:10 to Yuma to getting married in Paris, this Hollywood couple's decision to take it slow helped them develop the perfect relationship.
